</p>
<p>
1998 qualifies as ancient history, but if you want to see the <em>really</em> early days of PCWorld, you need to revisit our first year of magazine publishing, which <a href="http://www.pcworld.com/article/2027069/30-years-of-pcworld-30-pivotal-moments-in-pc-history.html">commenced in March 1983</a>?exactly 30 years ago.
</p>
